channel.title: TAG 2015 Agenda is now live!
channel.description:
The agenda is now live at http://www.aidtransparency.net/technicaladvisorygroup/tag-meetings/tag-meeting-may-2015/tag-2015-agenda
We're using Sched again so please either set up an account or revive your log in from last year and register for the sessions you want to attend.
We'll be adding in more detail about each session over the next day or two but the timings are all set now.
Looking forward to seeing you all in Ottawa!
Joni
